name: A Great Day in Brooklyn Postcard Set 1
description:
Four (4) postcard set includes three images by Jamel Shabazz and one shot of Shabazz in action, credited to Jamel Shabazz Photography Group, taken at DOPE SWAN's "A Great Day Brooklyn", held at the Brooklyn Museum of Art on June 8, 2008. 

Back of card lists name of the artwork and gives a brief description of the event with space for address and stamp.

Titles:

(1) Climbing PoeTree, (2) Lizz Fields, (3) Louis Reyes Rivera, (4) From Above (shot of Jamel Shabazz in action, taken from above).

Satin coated, 4” x 6”
